# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Foot Holics — website environment variables (Vercel serverless functions in /api)
#
# In PRODUCTION these are set in:
#   Vercel → Project Settings → Environment Variables
#
# For LOCAL development:
#   1. Copy this file:     cp .env.example .env.local
#   2. Fill in the value(s) below with your own keys
#   3. Run the site:       vercel dev        (serves the static site + /api endpoints)
#      Or pull from Vercel: vercel env pull .env.local
#
# NEVER commit a real key. `.env` and `.env.local` are gitignored; this template is not.
# (The bot has its own separate template at foot-holics-bot/.env.example.)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# api-football (api-sports.io) v3 key.
# Powers: /api/match-schedule, /api/match-detail, /api/match-info, /api/match-live
# (today's fixtures, match details, and live scores).
# Get a free key at https://www.api-football.com/  → dashboard.api-football.com
API_FOOTBALL_KEY=your_api_football_key_here
